\pard\sa80\f0\fs17\b 1. The Nature of Service (Transient Workspace)\b0\par
Astra/log is a Transient Workspace for rapid exploration and architectural planning of web applications.\par
\pard\li200\sa60\f0\fs16
\bullet  \b Zero-Persistence:\b0  Astra/log does not host, store, or collect user data. Every session is a clean slate; once a session is reset or the browser is closed, all filesystem data and chat history are permanently destroyed.\par
\bullet  \b Technical Consultant:\b0  The integrated AI is designed as a brainstorming and planning partner, not an automated coding agent.\par

